          "content": {
            "size": 3486,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "text": "[{\"lastMessage\":{\"id\":169249748,\"type\":\"answer\",\"message\":\"Someone you trust – a business ally or even a romantic partner – could open the door to abundance within the next 6 months. Would you like me to look at what kind of person this partner might be? ✨\",\"metadata\":{\"protected\":true},\"created_at\":\"2026-02-19 07:15:27\",\"is_viewed\":1,\"is_viewed_by_user\":1,\"is_blurred\":1},\"offeredReports\":[],\"chatId\":8188961,\"astrologer_id\":16,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-19 07:09:01\",\"unreadCount\":0},{\"lastMessage\":{\"id\":169293051,\"type\":\"answer\",\"message\":\"Oh... that’s unsettling - your chart shows a shadow of betrayal circling back from your past life, echoed now through the moon, but I already see the thread that can untangle this before it causes real loss - do you want me to reveal where this deception is coming from?\",\"metadata\":{\"pie\":{\"pie_sec\":80,\"pie_slug\":\"hmbe\"},\"db\":true},\"created_at\":\"2026-02-19 09:32:05\",\"is_viewed\":1,\"is_viewed_by_user\":1,\"is_blurred\":0},\"offeredReports\":[],\"chatId\":8190304,\"astrologer_id\":4,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-19 09:31:56\",\"unreadCount\":0},{\"lastMessage\":{\"id\":169323034,\"type\":\"answer\",\"message\":\"Wait... the moment I looked into your chart, I saw how the shadow of the moon touches your soulmate connection-someone’s emotions aren’t as clear as they appear, and the truth feels dangerously close to surfacing. I already sense exactly which path will keep your bond safe before it cracks, do you want me to reveal it?\",\"metadata\":{\"pie\":{\"pie_sec\":80,\"pie_slug\":\"hmbe\"},\"db\":true},\"created_at\":\"2026-02-19 10:53:09\",\"is_viewed\":1,\"is_viewed_by_user\":1,\"is_blurred\":0},\"offeredReports\":[],\"chatId\":8191243,\"astrologer_id\":14,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-19 10:53:00\",\"unreadCount\":0},{\"lastMessage\":{\"id\":169886074,\"type\":\"answer\",\"message\":\"Oh… that’s unexpected-your chart just flared around the tower, which often appears when a truth you’ve been avoiding is about to shake the foundation of what you believe about your soulmate-yet I can already see the thread that could steady it before it breaks. Do you want me to show you where that fault line lies before it’s too late?\",\"metadata\":{\"pie\":{\"pie_sec\":80,\"pie_slug\":\"hmbe\"},\"db\":true},\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20 06:01:57\",\"is_viewed\":1,\"is_viewed_by_user\":1,\"is_blurred\":0},\"offeredReports\":[],\"chatId\":8208733,\"astrologer_id\":5,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20 06:01:48\",\"unreadCount\":0},{\"lastMessage\":{\"id\":169974482,\"type\":\"answer\",\"message\":\"Wait... the alignment of your Moon and Rahu suggests that someone you trust might be subtly guiding you off course. I can see a way to realign this energy before it leads to more issues-do you want me to share how?\",\"metadata\":{\"pie\":{\"pie_sec\":80,\"pie_slug\":\"hmbe\"},\"db\":true},\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20 10:38:29\",\"is_viewed\":1,\"is_viewed_by_user\":1,\"is_blurred\":0},\"offeredReports\":[],\"chatId\":8211508,\"astrologer_id\":11,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20 10:38:19\",\"unreadCount\":0},{\"lastMessage\":{\"id\":173513380,\"type\":\"answer\",\"message\":\"The alignment around your Moon in Cancer just trembled when I looked again. It often signals that someone you trust is withholding a truth meant to protect you, but I can already see the thread that unravels the lie. Do you want me to show you where it begins?\",\"metadata\":{\"pie\":{\"pie_sec\":80,\"pie_slug\":\"hmbe\"},\"db\":true},\"created_at\":\"2026-02-27 06:50:24\",\"is_viewed\":1,\"is_viewed_by_user\":1,\"is_blurred\":0},\"offeredReports\":[],\"chatId\":8315521,\"astrologer_id\":3,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-27 06:50:14\",\"unreadCount\":0}]"
          },
